<Defs>
    <RulePackDef>
        <defName>Believes_Is_Trans</defName>
        <rulePack>
            <rulesStrings>
                <li>r_logentry->[INITIATOR_nameDef] believes that [RECIPIENT_nameDef] may be transgender.\n\n[what_happened].</li>
                
                <li>what_happened(didSex==false,cameOut==false)->[random_event]</li>
                <li>what_happened(didSex==false,cameOut==false)->[INITIATOR_nameDef] used [INITIATOR_possessive] [AdjectiveAny] transvestigating psychic powers and [random_event]</li>
                <li>what_happened(didSex==true,cameOut==false)->During their lovin' session, [sex_event]</li>
                
                <li>what_happened(cameOut==true)->[RECIPIENT_nameDef] came out to [INITIATOR_objective]. [comeOutPost]</li>
                
                <li>comeOutPost(isPositive==true)->[INITIATOR_nameDef] was rather respectful about it</li>
                <li>comeOutPost(isPositive==true)->[INITIATOR_nameDef] listened and nodded along as [RECIPIENT_nameDef] spoke [RECIPIENT_possessive] true feelings</li>

                <li>comeOutPost(isPositive==false)->[INITIATOR_nameDef] was shocked and enraged</li>
                <li>comeOutPost(isPositive==false)->[INITIATOR_nameDef] felt a fit of rage run rampage inside [INITIATOR_objective]self</li>
                
                <li>start_sex_event->[INITIATOR_nameDef] thought that</li>
                <li>start_sex_event->[INITIATOR_nameDef] noticed that</li>

                <li>sex_event->[start_sex_event] [RECIPIENT_nameDef]'s [sex_characteristic] was of another gender</li>
                <li>sex_event->[start_sex_event] [RECIPIENT_nameDef] did not love [INITIATOR_objective] like a [RECIPIENT_gender] would</li>
                <li>sex_event->[start_sex_event] [RECIPIENT_nameDef] [other_sex_verb] too much like a [RECIPIENT_otherGender]</li>

                <li>sex_event->[INITIATOR_nameDef] felt too good for [RECIPIENT_nameDef] to be a [RECIPIENT_gender]</li>
                <li>sex_event->[INITIATOR_nameDef] was [sex_verb] by [RECIPIENT_nameDef] too much for [RECIPIENT_objective] to be a [RECIPIENT_gender]</li>
                
                <li>sex_verb->bottomed</li>
                <li>sex_verb->topped</li>
                <li>sex_verb->plopped</li>
                <li>sex_verb->slammed</li>
                
                <li>other_sex_verb->moaned</li>
                <li>other_sex_verb->cried</li>
                <li>other_sex_verb->peed</li>
                <li>other_sex_verb->groaned</li>

                <li>sex_characteristic(mismatchedGenitalia==true,p=2)->genitalia</li>
                <li>sex_characteristic->[PersonalCharacteristic]</li>
                
                <li>random_event->[INITIATOR_pronoun] thought [RECIPIENT_nameDef] looked too [appearance]</li>
                <li>random_event(transvestigate==true)->[INITIATOR_nameDef] investigated [RECIPIENT_nameDef] doing something naughty using their [AdjectiveAny] [PersonalCharacteristic]. It seemed like something a [AdjectiveAny] [RECIPIENT_otherGender] would do</li>
